﻿@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
    ViewBag.Message = "Learn more about our student database system!";
}

<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <!-- Page Title -->
    <h2 id="title" class="text-center text-primary">@ViewBag.Title</h2>

    <!-- Subheading with a brief description -->
    <h3 class="text-center text-secondary">@ViewBag.Message</h3>

    <!-- Content Section with Information about the Database -->
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <!-- About the Database -->
                <p class="lead">
                    The student database system is designed to manage and store essential student information
                    in a structured and efficient way. It serves as a central repository for storing student details,
                    including personal information (surname, first name, age), contact details (telephone, address, email),
                    and academic performance (assessment marks and overall module mark).
                </p>

                <p>
                    This system allows administrators and authorized users to add, edit, and delete student records.
                    Each student's information is stored in a relational database, ensuring consistency and integrity.
                    With this system, users can easily retrieve and manage student data, making it ideal for educational institutions.
                </p>

                <p>
                    The system also supports secure data entry and validation, ensuring that all data entered is accurate and up-to-date.
                    Additionally, the system provides user-friendly interfaces for interacting with the database,
                    making it accessible to users with varying levels of technical expertise.
                </p>

                <!-- Features of the Database -->
                <h4 class="mt-4 text-primary">Key Features of the Database</h4>
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Centralized storage for student records.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Simple interfaces for adding, editing, and deleting student data.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Validation and error handling to ensure accurate data input.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Easy retrieval of student information by administrators.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Secure access and data management through role-based permissions.</li>
                </ul>

                <!-- Conclusion -->
                <p class="mt-4">
                    With its user-friendly design and robust functionality, the student database system ensures efficient
                    and secure management of student data, improving the workflow and data management process in educational environments.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
